        <p class="message">
          Thanks for joining our community of food lovers! Before you start exploring thousands of delicious recipes, 
          please verify your email address to complete your registration.
        </p>
        
        <div class="button-container">
          <a href="{{verifyLink}}" class="verify-button">Verify Email Address</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="divider"></div>
        
        <div class="features">
          <div class="feature-item">
            <div class="feature-icon">üç≥</div>
            <div class="feature-content">
              <h3>Discover Amazing Recipes</h3>
              <p>Browse thousands of recipes from cuisines around the world, from quick weeknight dinners to gourmet masterpieces.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="feature-item">
            <div class="feature-icon">üìù</div>
            <div class="feature-content">
              <h3>Share Your Creations</h3>
              <p>Upload your own recipes, share cooking tips, and build your culinary portfolio with beautiful photos.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="feature-item">
            <div class="feature-icon">‚ù§Ô∏è</div>
            <div class="feature-content">
              <h3>Save Your Favorites</h3>
              <p>Like and bookmark recipes you love, create custom collections, and never lose track of that perfect dish again.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="feature-item">
            <div class="feature-icon">üë•</div>
            <div class="feature-content">
              <h3>Join the Community</h3>
              <p>Follow talented chefs, connect with fellow food enthusiasts, and get inspired by their creations.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="info-box">
          <p>
            <strong>‚è± Quick heads up:</strong> This verification link will expire in <strong>24 hours</strong>.
          </p>
          <p style="margin-top: 8px;">
            If you didn't create an account with Recipe App, you can safely ignore this email.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="footer">
        <p>
          Need help getting started? Visit our <a href="#" style="color: #FF6B81; text-decoration: none;">Help Center</a> or reach us at support@recipeapp.com
        </p>
        <p style="margin-top: 8px;">
          ¬© 2025 Recipe App. All rights reserved.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
